K-Lite Codec Pack is a unique package of data converters (codecs) for compressing and decompressing audio and video files. K-Lite Codec Pack software package has been tested for viruses - it is absolutely safe.

Features of K-Lite Codec Pack

K-Lite Codec Pack for Windows 32 and 64 bit ensure that you won't have any problems with your media files. The unique codec pack lets you watch videos without stuttering, freezing or distorting the picture and listen to music with high sound quality.

K-Lite Codec Pack is designed in four versions: Basic, Standard, Full and Mega. We offer the latest version of the Mega codec pack with the built-in Media Player Classic, which combines the functions of the other versions of the software package. It additionally includes codecs for ACM and VFW video files.

Benefits of K-Lite Codec Pack

Set of 28 codecs for media files in different formats: MKV, AAC, FLAC, MP4, FLV and others;

improved image quality in photos and videos;

compatibility with other codec packs;

fast installation with the ability to customize components;

possibility of getting information about graphics, video and audio files;

automatic display of video subtitles;

Detection and removal of damaged codecs and filters;

convenient and simple Media Player Classic.

Download K-Lite Codec Pack for free from our site. You do not need to register and get a confirmation by SMS. Just download the APK-archive and install the codec pack on your computer.
